item.description: SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Data_Network_ContentDelivery_Account Datatype Description SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Data_Network_ContentDelivery_Account models usage data polled from the CDN system. Local counter The value stored for a data record. Type: float dateTime The time a data record was stored. Type: dateTime fileName The name of a file. This value is only populated in file-based bandwidth reports. Type: string popId The internal identifier of a CDN POP (Points of Presence).
